high_descs: Turn left and walk toward the white door, then turn left and approach the wooden shelf
Pick up the cardboard box from the shelf
Turn around and walk across to the floor lamp in the opposite corner
anns.task_desc: Examine the box under the light of the floor lamp

high_descs: Get off the chair and turn left.  Start walking forward to the wall and turn left.
Pick up the box from the table.
Turn left and carry the box to the opposite wall.  Turn left at the wall and walk to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a box and turn on a lamp

high_descs: Turn to your left and go across the room, to the door, then turn to your left and go to the book shelf across the room.
Pick up the cardboard box on the left side of the book shelf.
Turn to your left and go across the room, then turn left again and go to the lamp in the right corner, straight ahead.
Turn on the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the living room lamp.
